typeDescriptions.typeString:
literal_string "Hyperion, a decentralized map platform, aims to achieve the “One Map” vision - to provide an unified view of global map data and service, and to make it universally accessible just like a public utility for 10B people.
海伯利安是去中心化的地图生态。"
